short_description: Here's a look at the best snorkel packages available in Key West.
seo_description: Here, we’ve highlighted the best snorkel packages available in Key West based on what you’re looking for. The HonestEco Key West Dolphin Watch & Snorkel Eco Tour provides ample time –4.5 hours– to observe dolphins and snorkel. The tour travels through the quiet mangroves with small groups aboard an electric boat – perfect if you’re seeking an intimate excursion that’s more relaxing than other larger charters.
